name: myanmar-lottery-check
description: methods =========== findAll(seq): returns a promise that resolves to an array of lottery objects create({ lottery: ‘Sample Todo’ }): returns a promise that resolves to a newly created todo object findById(‘0123’): returns a promise that resolves to the todo object with provided id, e.g., ‘0123’.
